snippet.title: The Stanley Parable "Raphael Trailer"
snippet.description:
This is an actual email that the team received a few weeks ago. The Narrator thought it was too potent not to respond to.

This is also a perfect time to announce that the Narrator is taking questions from you, person on the internet! Email your question to askthenarrator@galactic-cafe.com and if he sees something in it perhaps he will respond.

This youtube channel will contain all of those videos and more. For more info on The Stanley Parable, direct your internet to http://www.stanleyparable.com
